      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. So if the parietal cells aren't producing enough intrinsic factor, or if the complex isn't forming correctly, is that what leads to the deficiency? How exactly does that \"missing\" B12 impact the system if it's not being absorbed properly?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
